John, if you would please play the video.

00:28:59.830 --> 00:29:01.580
That's Mr. Kinsey laying on the ground,

00:29:01.580 --> 00:29:06.580
and the other individual, sitting,

00:29:06.590 --> 00:29:08.910
is the person with the developmental

00:29:08.910 --> 00:29:10.310
and intellectual disability.

00:29:24.670 --> 00:29:26.092
- [Charles Kinsey] Arnaldo, please,

00:29:26.092 --> 00:29:28.044
please be still, Arnaldo.

00:29:28.044 --> 00:29:29.760
Get down, Arnaldo, lay
on your stomach, Arnaldo.

00:29:29.760 --> 00:29:31.843
- [Man Off Camera] He's
like, please don't shoot me.

