- [Woman Off Camera] But
why they shot the black boy

00:29:35.180 --> 00:29:36.290
and not the fat boy?

00:29:38.311 --> 00:29:40.197
- [Man Off Camera] Because
he was black, you know?

00:29:45.551 --> 00:29:48.010
- [Woman Off Camera] I
